Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat.\NHeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how wonderful to be here. Um our\Nlecture today is basically about peace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and um our ma our main um question that\Nwe ask ourselves is is peace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,external or is peace internal?\NSo I'm going to ask David to say just a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,couple words on that right now.\NIs peace external or is it internal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Peace is an internal affair. Yeah.\NSometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it leaks out into the world.\NPeace is an internal affair. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't turn off that music now,\NI'm going to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want peace and I want it right now.\NThat's a good way to start the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way here uh today\Nthe awareness came to mind that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,mind thinks but spirit knows.\N>> Oh that's good. The mind thinks but the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> mind thinks yeah thinks about things you\Nknow and the mind is really an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,instrument of the ego endlessly discuss\Nthings argue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and spirit just knows\Nsilently
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,>> that's that's really great\N>> spirit did that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,now might talk about it but it was\Nspirit that grabbed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My sweetheart's arm.\NSpirit is an instrument of God. So God
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,just grabbed your arm.\NSo you get in touch with your God
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,nature. Your spirit is your godly\Nnature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mind is the ego's nature.\NThe human life is of course
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind's spinning around but it's\Nreally the spirit that accounts for your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,existence.\NThe mind would like to convince you that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your survival is up to mind. Mind says\Nif you don't listen to me you won't make
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it to the end etc.\NUh but spirit is the one that knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,remember the time. Can you tell them\Nabout the truck when you were down in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Patagonia and and um you know you had\Nbroken down and the truck was smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh,\N>> tell them that story because that was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,more of the spirit than it was your\Nmind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:04:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh, that wasn't mind at all. No,\Nsometimes spirit uh uh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, I didn't hear thoughts. I just\Nknew I was in Patagonia, which is down
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,near the southern border, in my old\Ntruck, 68 or 64, whatever it is, big
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Willis truck.\NAnd uh I was many miles, 150 miles
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,probably from the nearest civilization.\NAnd I had parked the parked the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And uh and I came back to start the\Ntruck. I turned the key and smoke shot
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,out from under the hood.\NI thought, "My god, the engine is on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,fire." And here I am million miles of\Nnowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I already had heat exhaustion.\NI did I had very little energy to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with.\NAnd so here the engine is on fire and I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd run out of water.\NAnd uh I wasn't exactly an experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,desert hiker, you know, run out of\Nwater. So anyway, the smoke is pouring
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,out from under the hood.\NEven if you open the hood, you wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to see where it was coming from.\NAnd I thought, well, I guess you're
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,going to die here now.\NSo I sat back. I thought, well, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,time to leave. I'll leave.\NEvery time I've been close to death, I
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,sit around waiting for it to happen\Nand the miraculous always occurs. So
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway, I was all set to leave the\Nplanet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, an inner inner voice\Nsaid to me, "Well, I had a plastic cup
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with about this much coffee still in the\Nbottom, maybe half inch of coffee."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So,\Nan inner knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the inner knowingness was take this cup,\Nplastic polyester cup,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and take a screwdriver and jam it\Nthrough the bottom of the glove
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,compartment.\NSo, I opened the glove compartment. I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,took the screwdriver and I rammed it\Nthrough the bottom of the glove
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,compartment.\NWell, the bottom of the glove
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,compartment in your car, you think it's\Nmade of something solid, but it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just heavy duty cardboard. So, I\Nrammed it through this cardboard and I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,took this cup and I put it in there and\NI heard a sizzle and the fire went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's one reason I'm still here.\NBut anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a a knowingness\Nuh a nonverbal knowingness is the voice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of spirit. That's the voice of God.\NAnd people complain they've never spoken
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to God and God's been talking to him for\N20 years and they don't even realize
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is.\NI always thought it was Susie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's God talking to her. So I listen\Ncarefully when she speaks now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,respectfully.\N>> Okay, we're going to go ahead and start
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this. I think we've got everyone in. And\Num so the lecture today is on peace. We
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,want to welcome all of you. I know a lot\Nof you have come here from Canada,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,different areas, and we want to thank\Nyou for making that trip. And at this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,time, I'd like to introduce Dr. David R.\NHawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria and Excelsius Dio. Glory be to\Nthee, O Lord most high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.\NAnd uh what are we talking about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.\N>> Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh, peace. Right. Yes. I knew we were\Ntalking about something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have some slides on the subject\Nof peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Do you have a pen?\N>> I have a pen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> in case they need to take notes.\N>> That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.\Nthat that I that'll be a dollar. I I've
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,told that story before. I was way up in\Nthe Andes up near uh Machap Picchu. And
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,uh there wasn't anybody for miles and\Nmiles around, maybe I forget how many
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,thousand feet it was, over 10,000 ft.\Nand and I go through this narrow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,passageway and here's a a young girl\Nstand standing there and she's got a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,llama\Nand uh
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I said can I can I take your picture\Nwith that llama? She said that'll be a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,dollar.\NSo that's how I got into saying that'll
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,be a dollar.\NThat'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So now where is the first slides? Here\Nyou are at the map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh, the map of consciousness.\NUh, well, we use this thing as a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:10:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,pointer, don't we?\NIt's good for small children and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how many people are here for the\Nfirst time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.\NGod bless all the people who are here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for the first time. The thing about\Nbeing here for the first time is you can
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,only be here for the first time once.\NSo this is indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a memorable occasion in your life.\NI speak from humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I got more humility than\Nanybody I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you have to be able to read this.\NIs this the right height for this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it supposed to come down a little?\N>> No, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> That's it.\NOh, I can jump. That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. This is the map of\Nconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely well known and uh really known\Npretty much around the world. Now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,uh these are the historic levels of\Nconsciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the the ancient knowledge\Nuh well it's calibrated from 1 to a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:12:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,thousand and uh over on the left hand\Nside you see uh uh the view of God
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh your view of yourself\Nuh the level of enlightenment which
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates It's uh from 700 to a,000\Nand the emotion that goes with it and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the process that's going on in\Nconsciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that is extremely comprehensive\Nincludes just about everything that's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,possible to know.\NUh last night they had a something on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fox News about a famous murderer.\Nfamous murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,up right here. Here's where he\Ncalibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know where it calibrates without\Neven using the arm, but most serial
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,killers and all calibrate around 30. 30.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:13:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, anything below 200 is false.\NAnything below 200. So when we use the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,arm to find out whether a thing is true\Nor false,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,uh below 200 is falsehood and 200 and up\Nis truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use it on politicians.\N200 and up is truth. Uh and of course
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the the quick way to find out is that in\Nin the presence of truth the body goes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,strong.\NIn the presence of falsehood it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,weak.\NIt's so simple even an idiot can get
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that.\NYou get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:14:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a protoplasmic in my\Nunderstanding protoplasmic response
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that for life to survive it had to be\Nable to discern poison from food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So the little bacteria or little\Norganisms
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,had to have some way of knowing this\Nstuff here will kill you. This stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,here will make you grow. Those that\Ndidn't learn it are no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a basic\Nknowingness of life forms starting out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at the lowest forms of protoplasm\Nand going on up to the highest level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But with it you're capable of knowing\Nanything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the thing that's the most\Nmind-boggling of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the most mind-boggling thing of all,\Ntherefore, you won't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully.\N>> Uhoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is within an instant you can tell the\Ntruth about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything with a capital A,\Nanything now or ever. Anything anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe.\NAnything that ever occurred, anything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that's possible.\NYou can know the truth about anything in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,an instant.\NIt takes one instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how it works.\NWe have permission to do this here. This
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,crowd here calibrates over 350, 400,\N420. Holy cats. 440. Holy cats. 435.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,430.\NThis cal, this group here calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,over 430.\NOkay,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,let's do the United The United States\NCongress calibrates over 300
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,350.\NYou you calibrate higher than the United
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,States Congress. That's good enough for\Nstarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because it's a spiritually\Noriented group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To be spiritually oriented tends to lift\Nyour level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and throw you in the company of others\Nthat are like-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh people who are spiritually oriented\Ntend to gravitate towards each other and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,uh are attracted to each other and feel\Ncomfortable and at home with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So this is very famous this\Nthese levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:17:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called the map of consciousness\Nand it's uh printed in all the languages
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world 29 languages or 30\Nlanguages or something and is commonly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,known now throughout the world actually\Ndue to our own work and of course due to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it its practicality.\NSo you you don't have to read a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,book to get that a thing could by using\Nthe arm you can calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either truthful or it's not\Ntruthful. And if it is truthful, what
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,level of truth is it? Uh so this is\Nextremely useful. Now today what we're
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about is peace\Nwhich as a state of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 600.\NPeace as a way of being in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,one thing.\NPolitical peace is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:18:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But peace as a level of consciousness is\Nan extremely high state.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you have to give up the\Nattraction to all the other things that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,would pull you down.\NAs you see, shame and guilt, apathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,grief, fear, cravingness, anger,\Npridefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,are all in the lower\Nlower levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage is at 200.\NIf somebody's going to help me out, if
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the armed forces,\Nwho do I want to come and get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm laying there just been shot\Nabout to get blown up. Who do I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want somebody right here.\NI don't want somebody at pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want somebody who's going to\Ntalk to me and reason about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:19:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If they love me, that's fine.\NBut that's just uh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,flowery.\NI want somebody with courage.
