Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.52,0:35:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,great minds of history, you do. Except\Nthat now the far left has taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.28,0:35:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see what's wrong with the far\Nleft is that Karl Marx calibrates at
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.88,0:35:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,130.\NWhy is Karl Marx so low?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.59,0:35:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does not teach the truth. Truth is at\N200. Marxism is at 130. So the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.44,0:35:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the far-left calibrates low is because\Nit's based on the proposition of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.59,0:35:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,perpetrator and victim. It's a dualistic\Nperception.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.16,0:35:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And this dualistic perception projects\Nonto the world victim and perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're poor, it's got to be\Nsomebody's fault that they caused you to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.32,0:36:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,be poor. Not that you're lazy, didn't\Npay any attention in class, and are
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.56,0:36:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,drunk all the time. That's got nothing\Nto do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.64,0:36:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the halves are responsible for creating\Nthe have nots etc. All right. Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.92,0:36:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's tried as a social system\Nhasn't worked out anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.00,0:36:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have lots of politicians that's you\Nknow keep trying to put it onto us even
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.72,0:36:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,though it hasn't worked anywhere. Hasn't\Nworked anywhere. Show me some place
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.48,0:36:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,where it's worked in the world and I'll\Ngain some enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.24,0:36:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Next.\NUh this is uh very sophisticated
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.00,0:36:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,uh this has to do with a situation.\NUh there seems to be an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.04,0:36:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the event however only takes place\Nwithin a certain field of context.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.56,0:36:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So an event is defined actually by the\Nfield in which it seems to happen. It
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.80,0:37:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to happen. We'll go to the next\None. I shouldn't have put this one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.96,0:37:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not too good one. Uh\Nhere we have the difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.56,0:37:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,lower mind and higher mind. Now as we go\Nevolve from the animal kingdom, you now
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.32,0:37:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,come to uh the lower lower mind and uh\Nthe li the lower mind wants things. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.96,0:37:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,insensitive. It's callous. These are the\Npeople that go to jail all the time. all
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.92,0:37:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the time beating up people. Uh their\Nindifference to the suffering of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.04,0:37:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,totally insensitive,\Ncompletely selfish, you know, and they
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.28,0:37:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,depend on force\Nand uh higher mind is more
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.96,0:37:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,sophisticated. Higher mind, which is\Nmore typical of this audience, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.64,0:37:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is more sensitive. It tends to be\Nmerciful. It tends to serve all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.28,0:38:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's intelligent. So this is power.\NThis is power. This side actually has
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.76,0:38:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,power. And this side here depends on\Nforce. This depends on force.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.48,0:38:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I want somebody to follow me, I\Ndon't use a something to beat them beat
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.88,0:38:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,them up. I try to persuade them that\Nthis is the best way to go. Okay? We we
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.40,0:38:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,persuade people.\NUh
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.00,0:38:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,these are the levels of consciousness\Nin which form begins to register within
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.76,0:38:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,mind.\NThe first thing it runs into is that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.28,0:38:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which watches and experiences.\NThat's an aspect of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.44,0:38:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the observer, the witness which\Ndoesn't think. The light of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.07,0:38:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness\Narises out of the godhead
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.04,0:39:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,out of\Nout of God as creator arises the light
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.35,0:39:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.\NThough what we do is consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.52,0:39:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,research.\NWhat we're really doing is constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.11,0:39:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,researching what could otherwise be\Ncalled the mind of God which is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.07,0:39:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness. Consciousness\Nis infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.40,0:39:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh has no beginning and has no end\Nand has no limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.80,0:39:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's infinitely powerful.\NWith spiritual evolution, you get low
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.44,0:39:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,let go of thinkingness and you reach an\Ninner state of quietude.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.76,0:39:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that's mo easiest and most\Nobvious to get to reach is the observer,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.11,0:39:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness. You observe and witness,\Nbut you don't think anything about it or
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.35,0:39:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,say anything about it or argue anything\Nabout it. I observe someone sitting at
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.40,0:40:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the table. She looks peaceful.\NShe looks peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.76,0:40:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So I don't need the observer\Nwitness doesn't think about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.24,0:40:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So move on to the next. Then\Nwe have to become acquainted because you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.00,0:40:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,have to understand how you're going to\Nhave peace in a world uh without
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.24,0:40:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding the human condition.\NThe human brain left and right brain
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.96,0:40:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as your animal brain. Then your animal\Nbrain below 200 it sees something
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.11,0:40:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,happening\Ninstantly it goes it bypasses the cortex
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.20,0:40:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and goes directly to the emotions\Ngoes to the emotion emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.64,0:40:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So that's the emotional side\Nof the brain. It's really uh the animal
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.52,0:41:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,side. Below 200,\Nyou run by the animal brain which is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.48,0:41:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,into fight or flight. The alarm reaction\Ndisrupts the acupuncture meridians.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.80,0:41:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative muscle test response.\NAll right. The other side of the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.31,0:41:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the spiritual side. The right brain\Ndominance is nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.96,0:41:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the source of peace and we're\Ntalking about peace today. So what we're
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.96,0:41:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about is the release of\Nendorphins within your brain associated
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.64,0:41:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with positive emotions.\Nthe peaceful endorphins
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.00,0:41:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual side of your body\Nuh brings about healing, balances your
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.88,0:41:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,acupuncture system, and you get a\Npositive muscle test response.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.64,0:42:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're talking about today then\Nis
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.40,0:42:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,serenity, peacefulness\Nas a way of being in the world because
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.40,0:42:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that activates the condundalini energy,\Nthe spiritual energy uh to rise up into
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.72,0:42:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the right side of the brain and that\Nalters all your responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.04,0:42:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So a fearful person looks over there and\Nis frightened and a person who's more
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.88,0:42:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,into endorphins looks over there and is\Ninterested.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.96,0:42:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So the endorphins support life.\NOkay, next thing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.28,0:42:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness and social\Nproblems.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.59,0:42:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see here's the level of\Nconsciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.00,0:42:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,uh over here uh people or a community or\Na country or a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.28,0:43:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,neighborhood let's say\Nwhat is the rate of unemployment seeing
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.59,0:43:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as unemployment is very much in the news\Ntoday unemployment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.20,0:43:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the\N>> yeah anyway the rate of unemployment as
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.16,0:43:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you see increases the lower the level of\Nconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.24,0:43:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of unemployment does not\Ndecrease
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.48,0:43:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in direct align with\Nthe number of jobs available as everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.56,0:43:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,presumes.\NEverybody thinks the reason they're
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.35,0:43:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,unemployed is because there aren't any\Njobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.52,0:43:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see that the power is given to is\Ngiven outside the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.83,0:43:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm unemployed,\Nthere's only one reason, and I've been
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.96,0:43:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,unemployed.\NThere's only one reason I'm unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.28,0:44:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Me.\NSole cause of unemployment is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.16,0:44:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After World War II, there was no jobs.\NBut whenever there was no jobs, I always
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.59,0:44:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,had three or four of them. I drove cab\Nat night. I drove
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.44,0:44:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,cabb during the day or the bartender at\Nnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.52,0:44:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh if you're broke and you haven't got\Nany money, the quickest thing to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.16,0:44:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you go down any street. I'll tell nobody\Ncan ever complain that they're
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.80,0:44:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,unemployed after what I say next.\NYou want to run out, put your fingers in
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.31,0:44:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your ears.\NIf you want to listen to this, you can't
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.80,0:44:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,blame anybody anymore.\NI'll tell you what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.20,0:44:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret.\NYou go down any street.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.35,0:45:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You knock on doors.\NLady opens the door. You say, "You need
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.31,0:45:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,any windows washed today?"\NI've never gone more than three houses
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.76,0:45:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,without somebody employing me right on\Nthe spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.64,0:45:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,dollar window.\N20 minutes I made $10.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.68,0:45:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go down the next house. By noon I've\Nmade $95.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.88,0:45:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No income tax on it.\NDon't let me know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.59,0:45:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to be unemployed.\NSee, unless you're disabled, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.92,0:45:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're disabled like I am right now,\Nas you can see, I can barely walk
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.07,0:45:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,around.\NWhen you can't barely walk around, what
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.07,0:45:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,do you do? You give lectures for God's\Nsake.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.16,0:46:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You write a book,\Nsing a song, dance, be funny, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.80,0:46:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So unemployment then is a lack of uh\Ncreativity
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.44,0:46:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,uh a lack of awareness\Nand if you ask God dear God I need a job
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.64,0:46:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,please guide my guide my steps in the\Nright way then a job comes to you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.00,0:46:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,uh and failing that you knock on doors\Nit's un it's not possible to be
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.11,0:46:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,unemployed\Nanyway the rate of unemployment down
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.52,0:46:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,below here is 97%.\NIt's always those people's fault. Those
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.59,0:46:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,people's fault.\NThe rate of unemployment here is based
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.44,0:46:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,on blame and projecting\Nprojecting their power into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.20,0:46:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has the power over your employment?\NYou or the world? If you project it into
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.72,0:47:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the world, now you become a servant of\Nthe world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.44,0:47:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of unemployment amongst people\Nof higher energy fields is practically
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.44,0:47:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,0% as you see it goes up and I certainly\Nmust have been at least the 400s in
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.20,0:47:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,those days and uh unemployment there was\Nonly 7%. The rate of poverty goes up uh
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.72,0:47:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same way. The higher you go the\Nless the rate of poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.24,0:47:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Poverty is one thing. Being broke is\Nanother.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.68,0:47:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been broke a lot of times in my\Nlife, but I didn't consider it poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.40,0:47:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I considered it being broke.\NHow how is life happy or not happy? Down
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,here, these people, they're all unhappy.\NSo, you can see southernliness about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.00,0:47:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,life.\NUh what happens is your your rate of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.68,0:47:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,happiness decreases to almost 0%.\NThese people think they're getting away
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.68,0:48:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with something, but as you can see,\Nthey're all unhappy. All unhappy. And as
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.56,0:48:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,your consciousness level goes up, uh,\Nthe rate of happiness becomes almost
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.83,0:48:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,100%.\NAnd the rate of criminality shows the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.83,0:48:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,reverse. Of course, the higher the level\Nof consciousness, the rate of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.00,0:48:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,criminality is rather rather rare. And\Nas your consciousness level goes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.59,0:48:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of criminality\Nis close to 100%. Close to 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.00,0:48:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Every bum knows that if you go to sleep\Non the street, you wake up, your shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.07,0:48:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,are gone.\NSo always sleep on your shoes. Don't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.04,0:48:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,leave them on your feet. They'll take\Nthem off while you're asleep. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.04,0:48:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove next.\Nuh you see uh the uh susceptibility to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.80,0:48:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,AIDS correlates with the levels of\Nconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.28,0:49:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The lower the level of consciousness,\Nthe higher the rate of AIDS. Okay, we'll
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.16,0:49:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,go next.\NUm
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.83,0:49:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness and rate of\Nhappiness. We did that already. We see
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.88,0:49:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that\Npridefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.11,0:49:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,cuts your rate of happiness to 22%.\NAnd arrogance, anger, fear, all these
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.20,0:49:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,things cut your rate of happiness.\NCourage then from the level of truth on
