Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.11,0:49:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Next.\NUhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.16,0:49:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh these are the levels of consciousness\Nof great spiritual teachers. I just want
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.48,0:49:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you to know they're in several of the\Nbooks. Uh all the great spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.76,0:49:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,teachers uh worldwide and in and\Nthroughout history. Okay. Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.52,0:50:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Socrates was at 540.\NUh
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.11,0:50:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates at 540. Uhhuh.\NSo anyway, I just wanted you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.55,0:50:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're all available and they're\Nwritten in the book. You don't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.68,0:50:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,send us an email wanting to know about\Nsomehow we've got all these people
