Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.20,0:50:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,email about it.\NOkay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.48,0:50:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,\Noh,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.48,0:50:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there is the difference between essence\Nand perception. The difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.80,0:50:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,essence and perception. What a thing\Nlooks like is perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.48,0:50:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And it consists of projections, what you\Nproject onto a thing. Essence is what
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.40,0:50:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing really is within itself.\NSo here you see the wolf in sheep's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.07,0:50:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,clothing.\NThe wolf and sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.24,0:51:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside is the predator\Npredator who will steal from all the
