Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.00,0:51:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,private plane and uh villas around the\Nworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.48,0:51:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Where are we on this list?\N>> Are we gonna Okay, we're finally getting
